snippet.title: Kingdoms Forlorn - First Dungeon Playthrough
snippet.description: Gameplay and commentary of first 20 minutes of a dungeon in an upcoming open world,  first person, turn-based RPG, Kingdoms Forlorn. The video covers some core game mechanics like skills, inventory and equipment management, combat, puzzles....
